    "Processing The output of the prompting procedure (a.txt file) was converted to a.csv file with the appropriate column headers (e.g., \"Word\", \"Sentence\", \"Visual Strength\").",
    "Additionally, GPT-4's response (originally a string, e.g., \"1\") was converted to a number (e.g., 1).",
    "In three cases, no number could be identified in GPT-4's response: in each case, GPT-4's response indicated a refusal to answer the question.",
    "As decided in the pre-registration, those responses were excluded.",
    "Primary analysis: Assessing GPT-4's performance The primary question was whether GPT-4's ratings significantly co-varied with human ratings."
  ],
